.TH EasyTAG 1
.SH NAME
easytag \- tag editor for MP3 and Ogg Vorbis files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.na
.nh
.B easytag
.RI [options]
.br 
.B easytag
.RI [directory]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B EasyTAG
is a utility for viewing and editing tags for MP3, MP2, FLAC, Ogg Vorbis,
MP4/AAC, MusePack and Monkey's Audio files. Its simple and nice GTK+ 2
interface makes tagging easier under GNU/Linux.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP 
.B \-\-help
Display some short help
.TP 
.B \-\-version
Display version information
.TP 
.B [directory]
Choose the directory to open at startup. It can be either an absolute or a
relative path.

