.SH FILES
.PP 
EasyTAG will create a directory named easytag in your \fIXDG_CONFIG_HOME\fR
directory where it stores its configuration file and history files.
.br
\fI@prefix@/bin/easytag\fR: \fBEasyTAG\fR's location.
.br
\fI~/.config/easytag/easytagrc\fR: \fBEasyTAG\fR's configuration file.
.br

